snippet.title: The Best Quotes About Being Courageous (BRAVERY)
snippet.description:
The Best Quotes About Being Courageous. 

Courage is the choice and willingness to confront agony, pain, danger, uncertainty, or intimidation. Valor is courage or bravery, especially in battle. Courage quotes from vivid author are definitely worth your time.
